Actress and singer Simz Ngema left fans with their knees weak after she posted a breath-taking video on her dancing on Instagram. The Tholakhona singer has mentioned that music is her passion and she is now going for it! She gave a sterling performance at the Soulified Chillas All Black Everything show recently, and kept the crowd on their feet throughout the night. Simz has always been an entertainer, she has shared her dance moves on social media and she is always on point! In one of her post, she shared she is living her dreams that will keep her alive “Dad: you had dreams before you became Dumi’s wife. Those dreams will keep you alive. Remember who you were, remember your passions and start living your dream. Me: okay, let’s live” she wrote. Dad: you had dreams before you became Dumi’s wife. Those dreams will keep you alive. Remember who you were, remember your passions and start living your dream. Me: okay, let’s live! #QuingSimz #Tholakhona A post shared by  Simphiwe Ngema (@simzngema) on May 2, 2019 at 1:21am PDT Thank you to everyone that came out last night. I had so much fun with you guys. #soulifiedchillasallblack???????? #QuingSimz A post shared by  Simphiwe Ngema (@simzngema) on Apr 28, 2019 at 4:48am PDT  